211
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:11,640
Algun expert, d'acord?

212
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:14,640
No algú que busqui a Google en cinc minuts.

213
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:18,640
El tema de, per passar de Tajikistan a Pakistan,

214
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:20,640
