229
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,640
va passar aquella zona.

230
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:55,640
Diràs, pregunta-l'hi a ell.

231
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,640
Li he preguntat alguna vegada alguna cosa per Insta

232
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,640
